float cnoise(const vec3 c, const vec3 period) {
	vec3 ic1=floor(c);
	vec3 fc=c-ic1;
	ic1=mod(ic1, period);
	vec3 ic2=mod(ic1+1.0, period);
	vec3 d=(ic2-ic1)*vec3(XO, YO, ZO);
	float base=dot(ic1, vec3(XO, YO, ZO));
	vec4 s1=random(base+vec4(0.0,     d.y,     d.z,     d.y+d.z));
	vec4 s2=random(base+vec4(d.x, d.x+d.y, d.x+d.z, d.x+d.y+d.z));
	vec3 f=fc*fc*fc*(fc*(6.0*fc-15.0)+10.0);
	vec4 xi=mix(s1, s2, fc.x);
	return 1.0-2.0*mix(mix(xi.x, xi.y, fc.y), mix(xi.z, xi.w, fc.y), fc.z);

	vec3 wnReflection = reflect(wnVector, wnNormal);
	vec3 envColour = textureCube(envMapSampler, wnReflection).rgb;
	vec4 specularColour = sunColour*pow(clamp(-dot(sunDir, wnReflection), 0.0, 1.0), sunExponent);

	float fresnel = pow(1.0-abs(ndote), 1.0);
	vec4 surfaceColour = vec4(envColour, fresnel*0.75)+specularColour;
